COMMENT_TX: $Yankees challenged call that 7th pitch was a ball, claiming Gardner had been hit; call was upheld - ball, not hit by pitch
$CC Sabathia left game with injured hip

$Stanton got in rundown while Sanchez went to 3rd; Stanton ran past 3rd base down the line and was tagged; Orioles argued that it should be double play because Sanchez had passed Stanton; 3b umpire Kulpa ruled Stanton was out for abandoning the play, so no dp; Crew chief Meals agreed later that Kulpa was incorrect and Sanchez should have been out for passing Stanton; relevant rule is 5.06b
$Yankees challenged call that Torreyes was out at first to complete double play; call was overturned - forcout, no DP
